{"ts":"2026-05-22T15:44:33.944Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-6blp"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"pm plan: materialize creates dependency cycle; decision/discovery/validation flag mismatch; --steps all unsupported"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"Dogfood 2026-05-22: (1) CORRECTNESS: pm plan materialize generated a dependency cycle (generated task depends back on the plan; validate then flags the cycle). (2) UX: pm plan decision rejects --decision (actual flag --decision-text; likewise --discovery-text/--validation-text) with no did-you-mean suggestion. (3) pm plan materialize requires --steps and rejects --steps all; agents expect 'all' as the obvious default. Fix the cycle, add flag suggestions, support --steps all."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Issue"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":2},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":[]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-05-22T15:44:33.944Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-05-22T15:44:33.944Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"maintainer-agent"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-rnpb"}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"f74461c2312fa40875becde142cd0827083b1fad50aa2a3be5680dcb8f76a8af","message":""}
